<% provide(:title, "Help") %>

<h1>Help</h1>

<p>Welcome to StudyMates! This platform is designed to help professionals connect, collaborate, and grow together.</p>

<strong>Getting Started</strong>

<ul>
	<li>Create your profile and upload a photo</li>
	<li>Explore other users and connect with study partners</li>
	<li>Join discussions and share resources</li>
</ul>




<strong>Common Questions</strong>

<ul>
	<li>
		<p class="m-0">How do I connect with others?</p>
		<small>Browse users and send requests or start conversations in the rooms.</small>
	</li>
	<li>
		<p class="m-0">How do I update my profile?</p>
		<small>Go to your profile settings and edit your details anytime.</small>
	</li>
	<li>
		<p class="m-0">Having issues?</p>
		<small>Try refreshing the page or logging out and back in.</small>
	</li>
</ul>

<p>
	If you need further assistance, please reach out through the <%= link_to "Contact page", contact_path, class: "text-dark" %>.
</p>